Steps :

How to install Ansible:
1) Install EPEL Repo on Centos 7.x
# yum -y install epel-release ( Install epel using the following command )
# yum repolist ( Refresh repo by typing the following command )
2) Follow this link : https://www.cyberciti.biz/faq/installing-rhel-epel-repo-on-centos-redhat-7-x/
3) # sudo yum install ansible

How to connect to remote host using Ansible:
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-and-configure-ansible-on-centos-7

ansible all -m ping -u user --ask-pass
